SDLC
Planning - plan approach, risks
Analysis - define and document requirements, behaviors
Design - specifications and modules designed
Implementation - programming
Testing - should be done during all stages
Deployment - released, get feedback
Maintenance - fixes, use feedback for fixes

Regression - new patch, new feature
Sanity - minor change in code, don't execute full test plan/suite
Acceptance - testing done by client/end user. Beta test.
Functional - basic usability, do main functions work